summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Department of Parks and Recreation; authorizing the acquisition of portions of Lot 7, Block 10, Fairview Homestead Association, for the Benefit of Mechanics and Laborers, according to the plat thereof recorded in Volume 1 of Plats, page 119, in King County, Washington, for open space, park and recreation purposes; authorizing acceptance of the deeds; and authorizing the expenditure of funds previously appropriated from Capital Facility Bond proceeds for acquisition and related costs.
